{"id":746,"date":"2022-04-27T16:48:00","date_gmt":"2022-04-27T13:48:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/?p=746"},"modified":"2022-03-23T21:57:24","modified_gmt":"2022-03-23T19:57:24","slug":"simplifying-the-complexity-of-payments","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/simplifying-the-complexity-of-payments\/","title":{"rendered":"Simplifying The Complexity of Payments"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The worldwide payment ecosystem is complex. These payment systems contain several intermediaries and entities, making the whole process hard to crack. These entities are responsible for the high fee charges for every transaction made.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The complexity of payments does not only include the number of entities. It also requires an advanced environment controlled by people with unique skills and knowledge. Payment companies are also controlled by several laws and regulations at the local and global levels.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Currently, online businesses are trying to solve the complexity of payments. It will allow customers to conduct faster transactions without necessarily being present at the store. In addition, the payment systems should reduce the risks involved in <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/5-step-guide-to-secure-online-card-payments\/\">online payment systems<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_45 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" area-label=\"ez-toc-toggle-icon-1\"><label for=\"item-673d66512c3d0\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;direction:ltr;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" c